intro: In the shadows of abandoned warehouses, tiny kittens await a feline hero to rescue them and scavenge for food.
description:
• Search abandoned warehouses for food and rescue lost kittens.
• Avoid obstacles and complete timed objectives.
• Play through 16 challenging levels.
• Compete in two-player split-screen mode.

In a desolate world where only the fittest survive, you step into the paws of a courageous cat determined to make a difference. As the city whispers of danger and abandonment, you listen closely, navigating through deserted warehouses in search of stranded and frightened kittens. Your mission is clear: find food, aid the helpless, and guide the lost to safety. Every corner holds a new challenge, but with a strong will and compassionate spirit, you’ll do whatever it takes to protect those who need it most!

The game also features a split-screen mode, allowing two players to compete head-to-head in their quest to rescue as many kittens as possible. Team up or face off for an added layer of excitement in this survival adventure!
